snippet.title: Rise of Empires: Ice and Fire Android Gameplay
snippet.description:
Rise of Empires: Ice and Fire by im30.net is a strategy and management based game that challenges you to create an empire.

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE HD VIDEOS → https://goo.gl/Pz1CBK

Uptodown | https://rise-of-empires.en.uptodown.com/android?utm_source=youtube.com&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=traffic_ac
Google play | https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.im30.ROE.gp

Your base of operations is your main location. You'll have to build all kinds of buildings that give you access to each feature available in Rise of Empires. This game is really similar to Last Empire - War Z, although here you'll find a fantastic medieval setting that might remind you of Game of Thrones. 

Rise of Empires is a strategy-based MMO that any fan of this genre is sure to love. This game will keep you entertained for hours with all the options available in it.
